      "description": "This control groups the static and live-state signals that make Flux reconciliations reliable in practice: timeouts, dependency graphs, source freshness, interval configuration, and prune behavior. It is the \"good Flux config\" baseline that should inform both repo review and live-cluster triage.\n",
